            <p>
              We are carefully evaluating builders who meet our strict criteria for quality, 
              experience, and customer satisfaction. Our selected builder will have a proven 
              track record in northern New Hampshire custom home construction.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-4">
              The chosen builder will be dedicated to creating spaces that aren't just built 
              to last, but are designed to be loved, lived in, and cherished for generations 
              to come.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">
              Floor Plan Inspiration
            </h2>
